latestIgtvVideos.caption: Tomorrow: Lighten up with our latest color refresh.

There’s really not a bad Tree Flyer color in the bunch, but we’ve got to confess that we’re tickled pink by the newest member of the family. Find the limited edition Lux Pink in stores and online now in the US, UK, and Europe.

To celebrate Allgood™ Run Clubs, and the joy of running, we made some exclusive limited edition tees. Find them in any of our retail stores, and hey, maybe even go ahead and join an Allgood Run Club while you’re at it.
To all the Dads who <3 Allbirds. We <3 you right back.
Scenes from a summer day in Brooklyn and Coney Island, celebrating the Allbirds x Rosie Assoulin Sugar Sliders. Kind of dreamy, no? ☀️🍦🏝

Not sure what to look for when buying an indoor plant? Allgood™ Collective member @farmernick gives us three easy tips.

Psst, we’re opening our new flagship store in NYC this week and @farmermick is hosting two exclusive events. Take a peek at our stories to RSVP.

–
Over the course of the next few weeks, Allgood™ Collective members around the globe show us how they find nature in their everyday lives, inspiring us to do the same.
Get ready for a trip into the forest. T-minus one day and counting.

As part of our new resale marketplace, Allbirds ReRun™, we’re launching a trade-in program in a few of our U.S. stores. And when you trade in shoes in good condition, we’ll return the favor with $20 for you to put towards your purchase* before you head out. Not too shabby, eh? 

P.S. - Discover participating stores in our stories. If you’re not local to the three stores we’re piloting in, fear not, this is just the start — Our goal is to keep expanding trade-ins to more and more locations!

*Valid on any purchase of $98 or more

So what exactly is a carbon footprint? It's the amount of carbon dioxide equivalent that a product or activity releases into the atmosphere. 

How do we calculate it? We factor in everything— from materials sourced to end of product life—and from that we are able to assign each and every one of our products a carbon footprint. Our numbers keep you informed and ourselves accountable. 

Even though we are 100% carbon neutral now, we know there’s always room for improvement, which is why our Flight Plan outlines our game plan to reduce our carbon footprint to near zero by 2030. 

Check out our stories for a deeper dive into our Flight Plan and what makes up a carbon footprint. #TreadLighter

A moment of appreciation for the Tree Dasher, our OG running shoe made with natural materials like super comfy and breathable eucalyptus fiber. (And it’s now available at a super special price to make way for something new – you heard it here first! 👀)

Calling all fans of the iconic @staplepigeon. We’ve teamed up with @jeffstaple (again!) to design a new edition of the Allbirds X STAPLE Dasher. The end-to-end carbon footprint of this sneaker is on display, from production to transportation, amplifying the conversation around carbon footprints of what we wear.

P.S. The first colorway drops on the 13th, and the second on Jan 20th. Details to follow. If you're in the U.S., download our iOS app to make sure you don’t miss them. 

🎥: @kateisobelscott
